{"tid":517474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【感人父女】「你一直視我如己出」 18歲女呢份禮物搞喊繼父","createTime":"2018-01-02T10:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T10:20:29.000Z","uid":111253,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"9213101541b0bf4df6779b2ac6e0af036dc974e7","tid":517474,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:46:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180102/57651520\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57651520&d=nZRNgdHY6xtRP5JeSkPu0wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=e6db6232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180102%2F57651520&h=9b96e0b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180102/57651520</a>"},{"pid":"c4867a88659e4d3b24062fe0971fbfa3e494c383","tid":517474,"uid":41737,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92411cf6b345c31ebe51a88dff67915bd1483770","tid":517474,"uid":111253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/02/184718_c2967615bcc7c0a2fe170f45ec5de95b.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2F184718_c2967615bcc7c0a2fe170f45ec5de95b.jpeg&h=53464735&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9938d6cf9421fc270e10fc563cd9caca88f5d80","tid":517474,"uid":8253,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"樓主無圖就算仲要無文<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706901fe4cc24f80c56c27382e990f4d9f1a5775","tid":517474,"uid":111253,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:47:48.000Z","msg":"美國俄亥俄州18歲少女在去年平安夜送給繼父一份「可能是最好」的聖誕禮物，她送上一份收養文件，希望繼父正式收養她，成為她的合法監護人，「我有一個夢想，希望他收養我，我的聖誕禮物便是收養文件」。<br />\n<br />\n達布尼（Stephen Dabney）撫養了繼女瑪凱拉（Makayla Dabney）14年，平安夜當晚瑪凱拉將收養文件包裝成禮物送給繼父。當達布尼拆開一層又層的禮物盒、看到在內的收養文件後，瑪凱拉便向繼父表白：「我自5歲起便認識你&hellip;&hellip;你視我如己出。我想知道你是否願意收養我，這早應該發生了，改變我的名字及一切，。」<br />\n<br />\n達布尼聽罷繼女之言激動流淚，禁不住擁抱女兒，他感動道：「非常感謝，但你要停止你的讚美之詞，否則我會再次哭泣毀掉強人形象。」<br />\n<br />\n瑪凱拉稱自己曾發了一個夢，夢中要求達布尼收養她，故決定照辦煮碗。她直言：「那一刻令人難忘及興奮，因為我這個大計只有少數家人知道內情。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《獨立報》"},{"pid":"9a0a300d9b924f282dbca13f1429853c3ce478b4","tid":517474,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d562bcc83b10a7ce17ebd91434095fb3a74662b8","tid":517474,"uid":33756,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:03:26.000Z","msg":"想分遺產？"},{"pid":"1fd8066eaabd472264c9d8a541872510ca1f07be","tid":517474,"uid":28758,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:09:31.000Z","msg":"人地想養大你黎做嬌妻，你就去做人個女"},{"pid":"f1eee0ee9187721e565e833903cd3c531aa58aed","tid":517474,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:12:30.000Z","msg":"本身都係一家人？<br />\n搞咁多野"},{"pid":"0d8cc9f6826b7ff1706df9e01100f980cd4a8f74","tid":517474,"uid":73412,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"b9938d6cf9421fc270e10fc563cd9caca88f5d80","tid":517474,"uid":8253,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T10:47:43.000Z","msg":"樓主無圖就算仲要無文<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"樓主係正宗踢一腳，郁一郁嗰d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4085da517a50022d5f975322e2a7e9828106ad","tid":517474,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4867a886